                    },
                    "body": "Sorry, I didn't really say what I meant to.\r\n\r\nIt was more a question.  What output did you want the element to generate?  It's just not very clear what the new element is going to achieve in terms of output.\r\n\r\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=stryks",
                        "name": "stryks",
                        "displayName": "Peter Sharp",
